  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/a67141a2f9ee3f9267b5c88191f263f0.poster.avif?t=1665438209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/a67141a2f9ee3f9267b5c88191f263f0.webm?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/a67141a2f9ee3f9267b5c88191f263f0.mp4?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Morbid is an atmospheric <strong>psychological horror</strong> game; experienced as Senior Detective J. Taylor, unfold haunting and morbid events that will <u>question your sanity.</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/107006f00bbf7e351b95e9d4e0fb6ff4.poster.avif?t=1665438209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/107006f00bbf7e351b95e9d4e0fb6ff4.webm?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/107006f00bbf7e351b95e9d4e0fb6ff4.mp4?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dispatched by a chilling 911 call from a quiet suburban neighborhood, examine evidence and investigate the family's tragic and puzzling history.</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Atmospheric Environment:</strong> High-quality graphics, sounds, and a minimal user interface.<br></li><li><strong>Unique Lore:</strong> Morbid features a truly unique story and background.<br></li><li><strong>Investigate:</strong> Discover evidence to find clues and unravel the story.<br></li><li><strong>Dynamic:</strong> Find randomized items & clues within the environment.<br></li><li><strong>Interactive:</strong> Players can search containers, pick up items or objects, and interact with switches.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/efa64e086206b61ea94c785aa9d75b66.poster.avif?t=1665438209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/efa64e086206b61ea94c785aa9d75b66.webm?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/efa64e086206b61ea94c785aa9d75b66.mp4?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Early Access currently features core gameplay components of Morbid such as Player Interaction, Immersive Environment Detail, Atmospheric Sound, and AI Interaction.<br><br><strong><i>Why Early Access?</i></strong><br><i>“Morbid is currently playable and I'd like to gather feedback about what can be improved before release.</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/a67141a2f9ee3f9267b5c88191f263f0.poster.avif?t=1665438209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/a67141a2f9ee3f9267b5c88191f263f0.webm?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/a67141a2f9ee3f9267b5c88191f263f0.mp4?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Morbid is an atmospheric <strong>psychological horror</strong> game; experienced as Senior Detective J. Taylor, unfold haunting and morbid events that will <u>question your sanity.</u><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/107006f00bbf7e351b95e9d4e0fb6ff4.poster.avif?t=1665438209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/107006f00bbf7e351b95e9d4e0fb6ff4.webm?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/107006f00bbf7e351b95e9d4e0fb6ff4.mp4?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dispatched by a chilling 911 call from a quiet suburban neighborhood, examine evidence and investigate the family's tragic and puzzling history.</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Atmospheric Environment:</strong> High-quality graphics, sounds, and a minimal user interface.<br></li><li><strong>Unique Lore:</strong> Morbid features a truly unique story and background.<br></li><li><strong>Investigate:</strong> Discover evidence to find clues and unravel the story.<br></li><li><strong>Dynamic:</strong> Find randomized items & clues within the environment.<br></li><li><strong>Interactive:</strong> Players can search containers, pick up items or objects, and interact with switches.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/efa64e086206b61ea94c785aa9d75b66.poster.avif?t=1665438209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/efa64e086206b61ea94c785aa9d75b66.webm?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139100/extras/efa64e086206b61ea94c785aa9d75b66.mp4?t=1665438209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Early Access currently features core gameplay components of Morbid such as Player Interaction, Immersive Environment Detail, Atmospheric Sound, and AI Interaction.<br><br><strong><i>Why Early Access?</i></strong><br><i>“Morbid is currently playable and I'd like to gather feedback about what can be improved before release.</i>",
